Output docs/demo-dashboard.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/grove-demo/rails-app"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show
Type "./bin/grove"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Type "?"
Sleep 1s
Type "?"
Sleep 500ms
Type "q"
